result.title: 2016-2017 ACM-ICPC Northwestern European Regional Programming Contest (NWERC 2016)
result.content:
Hi everyone!

4 Europe Regional contests out of 5 was already passed. Depending official information 15 teams from Europe already passed to World Final. Congratulation!!!

I added one of them to Gym. On official website there is only test data and jury solutions. Unfortunately, there is no checkers. Feel free to fix bugs :)

Time constraints was assigned depending on execution time of jury solutions. On official contest there was very high time limits, maybe because of Kattis servers.
